The paper also discusses the use of multi-task learning, which is a common technique in machine learning, and this suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category. The paper also discusses the use of regression and classification tasks, which are common in artificial intelligence, suggesting that cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category. The paper also discusses the use of feature representations and end-to-end training, which are common in information retrieval, suggesting that cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category. Finally, the paper is about analyzing microscopy images, which suggests that cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category.
